            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Display retargeting: 3-5 per week. Brand awareness: 2-3 per day or 10-15 per week. Video campaigns: 1-2 per day. Start conservative and use data to adjust — raising a cap is easier than recovering from ad fatigue.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="faq-q-text">Do frequency caps hurt campaign performance?</span>
